  "theoryOfChange": "The Citizens Foundation USA (TCF-USA) outlines its approach to creating impact through its 'Education Program' and 'Our Work' sections on its website. This framework details how TCF ensures quality education, develops curriculum, provides intensive teacher and principal training, and implements a dedicated Quality Assurance (QA) team for monitoring and evaluation. The QA team conducts school visits, formal classroom observations, collects insights from stakeholders, and carries out centralized examinations to measure and analyze results, identify areas for improvement, and inform future strategy. The organization's annual reports also highlight the Board's engagement in strategic planning and monitoring of operating activities, tracking programs and activities against set parameters. Furthermore, TCF-USA's strategy includes a 'four-pronged approach' and 'three primary objectives' to address educational challenges and expand access, demonstrating a structured approach to achieving its mission.",
